===Pronunciation===
*(''adjective, noun''): ăbʹjĕkt, /ˈæbdʒɛkt/, /<tt>"{bdZEkt</tt>/ ''or'' ăbʹjĭkt, /ˈæbdʒɪkt/, /<tt>"{bdZIkt</tt>/
*(''verb''): ăbjĕktʹ, /æbˈdʒɛkt/, /<tt>{b"dZEkt</tt>/
